{"tid":1191273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平在俄羅斯出席經濟論壇期間差點跌倒","createTime":"2019-06-07T21:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T10:37:53.000Z","uid":127728,"like":516,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec24e7822416d517670eb42102a6784b6e4971d","tid":1191273,"uid":127728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T21:48:30.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平在俄羅斯出席經濟論壇期間，差點跌倒。<br />\n<br />\n習近平與俄羅斯總統普京一同在台上舉行論壇，在論壇完結時，習近平走到台前，與台下多名嘉賓握手，期間，習近平突然失平衝向前傾倒，身旁的保鑣即時將習近平扶住，習近平未有跌倒地上，他之後在台上繼續向出席人士揮手致意。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461529-20190608.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461529-20190608.htm&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW85ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=a52fbe07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461529-20190608.htm&h=3ccfa3b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461529-20190608.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rX_2VlWcUm0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrX_2VlWcUm0&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW85ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=4e0206db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rX_2VlWcUm0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7c2b731cdfe2c64ccae105fff60b62ac998606","tid":1191273,"uid":6604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T22:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb932125e06642edc4e5ea3605284d1bf04d7da","tid":1191273,"uid":30633,"like":114,"dislike":0,"score":114,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T22:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />腳痛"},{"pid":"024e8597